{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/Title.gif?t=1733959180\" /><strong>Sayonara Okaasan is an abstract and bittersweet interactive poem about life, death, and the meaning we find in between.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/apples.gif?t=1733959180\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring original hand-drawn art and music, this short title invites you into a mysterious world where every moment lingers with emotion. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/momkid.gif?t=1733959180\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Inspired by the creator\u2019s personal journey of watching their mother battle cancer,</strong> this solo work weaves themes of love and loss with artistic visuals and an almost stream-of-consciousness narrative. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/hutoLine.png?t=1733959180\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/features.gif?t=1733959180\" /> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Puzzle-solving elements that guide you through the game by following the words </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hand-drawn artwork </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original musical compositions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A mysterious and dream-like narrative </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bonus escape room-style puzzle unlocked by finding hidden items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Available in sev